A:"a"
O:a) "\\(\\frac{1}{\\alpha} + \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\beta}}\\) and \\(\\frac{1}{\\alpha} - \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\beta}}\\)", b) "\\(\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\alpha}} + \\frac{1}{\\beta}\\) and \\(\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\alpha}} - \\frac{1}{\\beta}\\)", c) "\\(\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\alpha}} + \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\beta}}\\) and \\(\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\alpha}} - \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{\\beta}}\\)", d) "\\(\\sqrt{\\alpha} + \\sqrt{\\beta}\\) and \\(\\sqrt{\\alpha} - \\sqrt{\\beta}\\)"
R:"Algebraic manipulation of coefficients yields option A."
}

